snippet.title: AOE3 Asian Dynasties Mobile 2010 (J2ME)
snippet.description:
Edit: unfortunately, I had to delete the first part record of this gameplay because of music copyright issues. Well, still this is a long enough video for you to see how we liked it back then in the old good Java gaming times. Unfortunately the newer Android/iOS-based smartphones are mostly unable to run this without an externally downloadable J2ME emulator like for example, phoneME or on PC the Mpowerplayer. There are plenty of sites on the Internet offering to download the game - search for "Age of Empires 3 Jar Download" in Google if you want to get the game and try it out on your own.

Gameplay in Age of Empires III: The Asian Dynasties, w/ the OST ingame music from Age of Empires II: The Conquerors by Stephen Rippy. Enjoy!
